snippet.title: Click Legends
snippet.description:
Click legends (Available on STEAM), gameplay trailer! A clicker Incremental/Management game for $2.99. 

Join your Legendary Heroes in a battle for strength in CLICK LEGENDS. A Clicker - Incremental - Management game.  Battle your way through a variety of enemies by leveling up your heroes, empowering them, and finding them equipment! Click your way to victory!
